# Multi-wallet usage examples:
# - Use different mnemonics for different roles
# - Administrator wallet: For protocol management and admin operations
# - Investor wallet: For investment transactions and token purchases
# - Project wallet: For project-specific operations and token management
# - Any custom role names can be used (e.g., oracle, validator, etc.)
#
# The system will automatically detect and load all wallet_mnemonic_* variables
